strings: <voice_0x010010C7><se_def>*: Halt! Where do you think you're going!?
<voice_0x010010C8><se_def>*: You didn't really think we'd let an odd bunch of flea-bitten, ill-begotten, ne'er-do-well weirdos like you through, did you!? SCRAM!

<voice_0x010010C9><se_low>Yangus: An odd bunch!? Mind yer manners!
Wot's odd about us, eh!?
Come on then, out wiv it. I dare ya!

<voice_0x010010CA><se_def>Angelo: I don't think there's any need for that tone.
We're no more weird than any other travellers.

<voice_0x010010CB><se_high>Jessica: I think you'd better apologise!
We've done nothing to deserve that little tirade!
We're just normal travellers.
<voice_0x010010CC><se_low>King Trode: How dare you!? What a nerve calling us all that before we've even uttered a word!
<voice_0x010010CD><se_low>King Trode: You should at least give us an explanation as to what exactly you think is so unsavoury about us!
<voice_0x010010CE><se_def>*: I don't care what you say, I'm not letting you through. I wasn't going to single anyone out, but look at your driver!

<voice_0x010010CF><se_def>*: You're the worst one!
You look just like a monster if you ask me!

<voice_0x010010D0><se_def>*: You've hardly got grounds for complaint,
travelling around with a man that looks like
a monster!
<voice_0x010010D1><se_def>*: You should be grateful you're not under arrest! Now get out of here before I change my mind!
